OL,7,FRos was infected with contaminated
OL,8,Fblood products as a child, to tackle a
OL,9,Frare bleeding disorder called Von
OL,10,FWillebrand disease.
OL,12,FShe found out those blood products had
OL,13,Finfected her with hepatitis C aged 19
OL,14,Fbut doesn't know when exactly she was
OL,15,Finfected as her medical notes have
OL,16,Fbeen lost.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/11
