OL,3,CInfected blood survivor demands: 'No
OL,4,Cmore platitudes, we need to hear
OL,5,Canswers'
OL,7,FYet through all this, Ros and her
OL,8,Fmother have been campaigning and
OL,9,Ffighting for the truth.
OL,11,FDoing that, Ros says, is like another
OL,12,Fthing she has had to battle: "I was
OL,13,Finfected with contaminated blood, that
OL,14,Fwas then in my body until I had
OL,15,Ftreatment that then wrecked my body
OL,16,Fand my mind.
OL,18,F"So I had the virus that was then
OL,19,Firradiated by the treatment, that was
OL,20,Fthen in there doing all the damage.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/11
