OL,3,CInfected blood survivor demands: 'No
OL,4,Cmore platitudes, we need to hear
OL,5,Canswers'
OL,7,F"And then you've got this fight.
OL,9,F"This trying to be heard...and you're
OL,10,Fkind of carrying that, it's almost
OL,11,Fanother infection, another thing."
OL,13,FThe pair have accrued thousands of
OL,14,Fdocuments in their quest for what
OL,15,Fexactly caused the blood scandal, and
OL,16,Fwho knew what and when.
OL,18,FSome letters date back to 1975, and
OL,19,Fshow that even then the risks between
OL,20,Fthe blood and infection was known.
