OL,7,FOther documents show that some
OL,8,Fpatients were given contaminated blood
OL,9,Fas a test to see what impact they
OL,10,Fwould have.
OL,12,FStanding looking at the documents in
OL,13,Ftheir dining room, it isn't hard to
OL,14,Fsee why this has been called 'worst
OL,15,Ftreatment disaster in the history of
OL,16,Fthe NHS.'
