OL,3,CInfected blood survivor demands: 'No
OL,4,Cmore platitudes, we need to hear
OL,5,Canswers'
OL,7,FThat is what Sir Brian Langstaff has
OL,8,Fbeen looking into since 2018, and Ros
OL,9,Fand Juliet hope the publishing of his
OL,10,Freport on Monday will be the beginning
OL,11,Fof the end of their fight.
OL,13,FThey want to hear the truth, even
OL,14,Fthough they know it won't necessarily
OL,15,Fbe easy. And after the truth they want
OL,16,Fproper compensation, and a heartfelt
OL,17,Fapology.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/11
