OL,3,CInfected blood survivor demands: 'No
OL,4,Cmore platitudes, we need to hear
OL,5,Canswers'
OL,7,FThe government has said they accept
OL,8,Fthe "moral case" for compensation and
OL,9,Finterim payouts of #100,000 have
OL,10,Falready been made to about 4,000
OL,11,Fvictims and bereaved partners.
OL,13,FBut Ros says that they need more than
OL,14,Fthis: "What we need is for the state
OL,15,Fto actually accept, recognise and
OL,16,Facknowledge what did go wrong rather
OL,17,Fthan saying 'we did the best at the
OL,18,Ftime and because we think morally we
OL,19,Fshould do something, we'll do
OL,20,Fsomething'.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G8/11
