OL,3,CInfected blood survivor demands: 'No
OL,4,Cmore platitudes, we need to hear
OL,5,Canswers'
OL,7,F"It is actually about saying, 'We got
OL,8,Fthis monumentally wrong, the fact that
OL,9,Fthis is the worst treatment disaster
OL,10,Fin the NHS and actually it's down to
OL,11,Fwhat we did, what previous
OL,12,Fadministrations did.
OL,14,F"That needs to be admitted and
OL,15,Facknowledged, people need to stand up
OL,16,Fand say, from the heart how sorry they
OL,17,Fare about that."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G9/11
