OL,7,FRos adds the recommendations Sir Brian
OL,8,FLangstaff made to widen the
OL,9,Fcompensation scheme to include
OL,10,Forphaned children and bereaved parents
OL,11,Fmust be actioned as, until everyone is
OL,12,Ftreated fairly then she won't be able
OL,13,Fto move on.
OL,15,FAnd moving on is what Ros wants to do,
OL,16,Fand quite frankly what she deserves to
OL,17,Fdo. Aged 50 she feels she doesn't
OL,18,Freally know who she is without the
OL,19,Ffight for justice.
