OL,7,FAs her Mum puts it "I think of all the
OL,8,Fthings I could have been doing, and
OL,9,FRos could have been doing, but I've
OL,10,Fspent all the time doing all this
OL,11,Fother stuff.'
OL,13,F"It's time they were able to stop
OL,14,F'other stuff' and start living."
